		max-width: 1300px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 20px;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		height: 100%;
	}

	.top-bar-left {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0;
		flex: 1;
	}

	/* Quote of the Day */
